org.apache.paimon.operation

Class MergeFileSplitRead

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.operation.MergeFileSplitRead
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SplitRead<KeyValue>

    public class MergeFileSplitRead
extends Object
implements SplitRead<KeyValue>
    An implementation for KeyValueFileStore, this class handle LSM merging and changelog row kind things, it will force reading fields such as sequence and row_kind.
    See Also:
    If in batch mode and reading raw files, it is recommended to use this read.
